_sText:
That is my first Map, I used my own Textures and add a little bit Minimal Music in it. Its a freaking Pro Map, with mpbhops, which have 4 (maybe long) Level (Red, Darkblue, Lightblue and Green) and a Longjump Stage after finished it.
I think this map could be good training to get better bhop skills.

Hope you enjoy. Have Fun.
